metadata.name: Masami
metadata.description:
Masami (マサミ)

Searing flame Masami, warrior from dragonoid race. She is the owner of dragonic dark sword, legendary weapon that brings devastation to enemy. Her sword art enhances high level fire element skill to her blade that why people title her “Searing flame”. She will be happy to join your party if you fed her with plenty of meats along your mission. 
Art Concept
Red hair girl with dragon features like horns, metalic scales, reptile eyes in gorgeous dark kimono with beautiful flower pattern while holding powerful black demonic sword
 Resolution 2480 x 3508 pixels 300 dpi
